These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-1::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  photographer, teacher
There are 2 different favourite colors: red, amber
1. the person who likes red is on the far left##1
2. the person who likes amber is not the teacher##6

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |
| Food    | teacher   | photographer  |
| Sport   | red | amber |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-2::.
There are 2 different nationalities: russian, polish
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: volleyball, rugby
1. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
2. the person who's sport is volleyball is not the polish##6

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1   |     2      |
| Food   | russian | polish      |
| Pet    | volleyball  | rugby |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-3::.
