.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-20::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: skydiving, video-games
The people use 2 different means of transport: taxi, quad-bike
1. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
2. the person driving the taxi is not the person who's hobby is video-games##6

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2     |
| Pet     | video-games | skydiving      |
| Sport   | quad-bike | taxi |

 